8b86df28ba577b09f16da4915b3c7da8020fc9c3","tid":271190,"uid":61211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地無大學學位都好 有流利既英文都好基本<br />\n講下點樣小小咁起好佢<br />\n我自己就記生字差同成日用中文諗句子轉做英文就錯<br />\n好想學好啲英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由興趣開始學生字囉，大部份遊戲都有英文wiki，咪由果度開始囉"},{"pid":"ff45bbb1aeffae0e511ead45a024f2f455863c09","tid":271190,"uid":45000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地無大學學位都好 有流利既英文都好基本<br />\n講下點樣小小咁起好佢<br />\n我自己就記生字差同成日用中文諗句子轉做英文就錯<br />\n好想學好啲英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<br />\n本身U grad,但讀science同本身英文已經屎, 出到黎做野又冇乜機會用英文,更加屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eddd82ffd10f6a0f8397bb51ec073d58244f69","tid":271190,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c899418a1ee13b084853e47838e54d55c041d51","tid":271190,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:37:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5548ba853e0dabce87349edbab9be00c52a49466","tid":271190,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:41:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b300d261b6d804f0e4d87ce910e77d08d849f16","tid":271190,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86365d1fb881efa82b005d127e69cd7f7c2f8f0b","tid":271190,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"多d睇有中英字幕既戲/片"},{"pid":"bceaebc09cf7716976708204e277b69fb8f754f0","tid":271190,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99c0efc8f3ce8ae27be04223e249df8bc4c4acd4","tid":271190,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/search/query?term_1=%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E&amp;theme=WEB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcat.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fsearch%2Fquery%3Fterm_1%3D%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%26theme%3DWEB&d=FscGbLe7T1TTAA0VB6MmGC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=68bde053\" target=\"_blank\">https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/search/query?term_1=%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E&amp;theme=WEB</a></blockquote><br />\n真係好咩</blockquote><br />\n背下Ｄ常用句子<br />\n起碼你旅行會用得番</blockquote><br />\nCan I be <strong>excused?</strong> <br />\n粗魯Ｄ: Can I go to toilets?<br />\n呢Ｄ日常野一定要識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExcuse 係一個名詞黎，原句 can I be excuse 直譯做 我可以做藉口嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCan I be excused 《-  be excused 即係短暫離開<br />\n<br />\n最好都係用 May I be excused 有禮貌啲"},{"pid":"90715f056139bd93774f33ac317e999005df42a4","tid":271190,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:01:11.000Z","msg":"小學程度想學返起留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都有睇下BuzzFeed 同VoiceTube <br />\n硬係覺得好多記完 到時要用會講唔返既感覺"},{"pid":"7f0a4c31db17f0cfc6d7937384a03bb9d9634c40","tid":271190,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37ee06d0ae2b36446b2755607caf584b6d0a828c","tid":271190,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"youtube應該好多教日常英文嘅片<br />\n<br />\n最緊要KEEP住睇同講 <br />\n<br />\n想練埋口音就聽bbc(淨聽就OK 唔使刻意明 當然明係最好啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22e8300c6553e5bf5a89962235c4b4f89ebee74","tid":271190,"uid":88928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"我都係睇YouTube多， 除左樓上巴打講既X Factor我都會睇British Got Talent <br />\n同American Got Talent 呢啲類似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有會睇外國YouTuber啲Gaming同9up睇得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽得多真心英文會有進步 <br />\n我個人無興趣既野會唔想知， 不過睇YouTube唔會有呢個問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀同寫唔想上堂既可以上網睇人地寫既blog啊文啊呢啲， BBC news 個個都講我唔使重複啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw最近發現有一個幾好既網，都係人地推比我， 本身好似係出英文教材既公司， 叫 Learn Hot English，我通常會睇個網既blog（因為免費哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n巴打可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd86d9a24d28db026c11c24f60d0e0c3252dbb2","tid":271190,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"早排發現自己CL音係發唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nClaim clear climb 全部發唔到"},{"pid":"8b023728cdaac6b29909f42b71d33fb75e9dfa2d","tid":271190,"uid":88928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係睇YouTube多， 除左樓上巴打講既X Factor我都會睇British Got Talent <br />\n同American Got Talent 呢啲類似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有會睇外國YouTuber啲Gaming同9up睇得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽得多真心英文會有進步 <br />\n我個人無興趣既野會唔想知， 不過睇YouTube唔會有呢個問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀同寫唔想上堂既可以上網睇人地寫既blog啊文啊呢啲， BBC news 個個都講我唔使重複啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw最近發現有一個幾好既網，都係人地推比我， 本身好似係出英文教材既公司， 叫 Learn Hot English，我通常會睇個網既blog（因為免費哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n巴打可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打係講Buzzfeed我見隔離po有講Xfactor就打Xfactor，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf04355183f3b29ee99ffbc68225cfc259bfa9f","tid":271190,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"一年<br />\n日日睇聽用寫英文<br />\n日常生活所有野用英文<br />\n<br />\n一日講/聽過千句英文<br />\n自然識<br />\n<br />\n問題係好少人做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cccd73165157d6d7424b0e87dff7eaa00d41d3","tid":271190,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"睇美劇...<br />\n睇下英文字幕 (中文有時大陸尻譯)"},{"pid":"d4716aa2ef9e7c62a1a61c0906bf4eded9afeb18","tid":271190,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"去拎the standard睇, 有某啲位置專柵有趣<br />\n<br />\n聽英文歌要睇歌詞, 查字典"},{"pid":"eefe03c8f4db9c737c239449595c187149293e3b","tid":271190,"uid":6024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打話一年聽說讀寫都用英文 好難喎<br />\n朋友個個都係廣東話架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以聽下歌既但我唔知佢講咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}